# üèõÔ∏è Pantheon-Prime

## A Unified Framework for Cross-Domain Reasoning, Symbolic Engines, and Future-Facing Cognitive Architecture

Pantheon-Prime is an open research repository exploring **high-bandwidth idea generation, cross-domain synthesis, and long-horizon cognitive architectures.**

It combines techniques from:
* Computational reasoning and systems engineering
* Symbolic AI and memetics
* Narrative structure and cognitive science
* Mathematics, information theory, and creative engines
* Temporal modeling

Pantheon-Prime is not a product. It is a sandbox for:

> ‚ÄúPlanting seeds whose full utility becomes clear only when future technology catches up.‚Äù

Many of the concepts here are **X-Gap oriented**‚Äîdesigned to activate when an enabling discovery, model capability, or computational primitive emerges.

